Snoop on a serial line, using two serial ports.

Requires a breakout box that connects in the middle of a serial line, and
tees the TXD line to RXD on one of the listening serial ports, and RXD to
RXD on the other listening serial port, as well as teeing the modem control
lines in the manner pictured below.

                 RXD -------+------------------------- RXD
    DCE                     |                               DTE
                 TXD ----------+---------------------- TXD
                            |  |
                 CTS -------------+------------------- CTS
                            |  |  |
                 RTS ----------------+---------------- RTS
                            |  |  |  |
                 DSR -------------------+------------- DSR
                            |  |  |  |  |
                 DTR ----------------------+---------- DTR
                            |  |  |  |  |  |
                 DCD -------------------------+------- DCD
                            |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                 RI  ---------------------------+----- RI
                            |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                 GND ----+---------------------------- GND
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                         |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
     Port 0      RXD ----|--+  +---------------------- RXD     Port 1
  (DCE Monitor)          |        |  |  |  |  |  |          (DTE Monitor)
                 TXD     |        |  |  |  |  |  |     TXD
                         |        |  |  |  |  |  |
                 CTS ----|--------+  +---------------- CTS
                         |              |  |  |  |
                 RTS     |              |  |  |  |     RTS
                         |              |  |  |  |
                 DSR ----|--------------+  +---------- DSR
                         |                    |  |
                 DTR     |                    |  |     DTR
                         |                    |  |
                 DCD ----|--------------------+  |     DCD
                         |                       |
                 RI  ----|-----------------------+     RI
                         |
                 GND ----+---------------------------- GND

The software requires that port 0 (the first port specified on the command
line) be connected to the DCE monitor port on the breakout box, and port 1
(the second port specified on the command line) be connected to the DTE
monitor port.

